DESCRIPTION:If you've always felt like you didn't know how to look at art
 \, you've come to the right place\; bring your lunch and hop on Zoom as w
 e show you a tried-and-true method for looking at things.  On the second 
 Monday of each month\, join Eskenazi Museum of Art's resident Arts-based 
 Wellness Experiences Manager Keaton Evans-Black to look at and talk about
  a piece of art from the IU museum collections using the see\, think\, wo
 nder framework.  No previous art experience necessary! Meeting URL: https
 ://iu.zoom.us/j/6082812369
